name: A poor torn heart, a tattered heart
description: This image is the result of 100 iterations of running these opening lines of Emily Dickinson's poem, "A poor torn heart, a tattered heart", through a modified version of BigSleep, a script using OpenAI's CLIP and BigGAN to generate images from just lines. My work focuses on examining how computer models trained using natural language processing to accurately classify images from text then interpret lines of poetry.
